methods.name: public abstract Iterator<Charset> charsets()
methods.comment:
* Creates an iterator that iterates over the charsets supported by this
     * provider.  This method is used in the implementation of the {@link
     * java.nio.charset.Charset#availableCharsets Charset.availableCharsets}
     * method.
     *
     * @return  The new iterator

methods.name: public abstract Charset charsetForName(String charsetName)
methods.comment:
* Retrieves a charset for the given charset name.
     *
     * @param  charsetName
     *         The name of the requested charset; may be either
     *         a canonical name or an alias
     *
     * @return  A charset object for the named charset,
     *          or {@code null} if the named charset
     *          is not supported by this provider
